# Governance surface for the autonomous Jules routines.
# Routines may read these but must never merge changes to them: require an
# explicit human review. Enforced only when branch protection has
# "Require review from Code Owners" enabled for the default branch.
#
# Scoped deliberately NOT to all of .github/workflows/ so dependabot's
# github-actions bumps to other workflows are not gated.

/AGENTS.md                          @ryusoh
/.jules/                            @ryusoh
/scripts/agents/                    @ryusoh
/.github/CODEOWNERS                 @ryusoh
/.github/workflows/commit-lint.yml  @ryusoh
